20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-6-year-old-only-has-tantrums-around-his-grandparents-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekids%20tantrum%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20they%20don't%20get%20their%20way%20or%20they're%20bored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPick%20up%20a%20toy.%20Invite%20him%20to%20play%20with%20you.%20You%20just%20want%20to%20redirect%20his%20focus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20always%20known%20Jason%20would%20be%20an%20incredible%20father%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20I'd%20married%20a%20bona%20fide%20baby%20whisperer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERedirecting%20my%20toddler's%20attention%20resembled%20my%20work%20in%20politics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEthan%20had%20a%20few%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-parenting-tip-i-learned-from-dog-whisperer-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeltdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20every%20time%20I%20heard%20my%20Jedi%20Master's%20words%20echo%20in%20my%20ears%3A%20Redirect%20his%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Mark%20Daley%20sitting%20in%20a%20director's%20chair%2C%20resting%20his%20chin%20on%20his%20left%20hand.%20He%20has%20brown%20hair%2C%20dark%20eyes%2C%20and%20wears%20brown%20rimmed%20glasses%20and%20a%20white%20collared%20shirt.%20He%20rests%20his%20other%20hand%20on%20his%20knee%20and%20smiles%20slightly.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65737aad7a3c8094d5db4727%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222736%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mark%20Daugherty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20hang%20of%20it%20once%20I%20realized%20managing%20a%20toddler's%20attention%20was%20similar%20to%20the%20redirection%20work%20I'd%20done%20for%20years%20as%20a%20press%20secretary.%20%26quot%3BSenator%20Clinton%20voted%20against%20the%20bill%20because%20it%20would%20have%20increased%20gas%20prices%20for%20New%20Yorkers%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20she%20has%20been%20a%20longtime%20supporter%20of%20ethanol%20and%20other%20alternative%20fuels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20were%20teaching%20our%20foster%20children%20emotional%20safety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20yet%20have%20the%20language%20for%2C%20what%20Jason%20was%20teaching%20me%20with%20his%20baby%20whispering%2C%20was%20how%20to%20establish%20the%20basis%20for%20emotional%20safety.%20Ethan%20had%20displayed%20big%20feelings%20and%20we%20didn't%20go%20away.%20We%20didn't%20react%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdr-becky-kennedys-tips-for-dealing-with-kids-feelings-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig%20feelings%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20our%20own.%20We%20didn't%20meet%20his%20yelling%20with%20our%20yelling.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%2C%20but%20only%20because%20I%20was%20panicking%20and%20didn't%20know%20what%20else%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntellectually%20I%20knew%20this%20was%20normal%20behavior%20for%20any%20toddler%2C%20and%20I%20suspected%2C%20extremely%20normal%20for%20any%20child%20going%20through%20trauma%20and%20significant%20change.%20But%20I%20learned%20during%20these%20tantrums%20that%20perhaps%20even%20more%20than%20my%20obligation%20to%20provide%20a%20physically%20safe%20space%20for%20these%20boys%20was%20my%20obligation%20to%20create%20an%20emotionally%20safe%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20them%20to%20know%20they%20were%20loved.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20know%20they%20were%20safe%20and%20to%20feel%20every%20big%20feeling%20they%20had.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20know%20that%20Jason%20and%20I%20weren't%20going%20anywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20truth%2C%20I%20was%20the%20one%20not%20feeling%20emotionally%20safe%2C%20because%20I%20couldn't%20have%20the%20same%20assurance%20that%20they%20would%20never%20leave%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20from%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.simonandschuster.com%2Fbooks%2FSafe%2FMark-Daley%2F9781668008782%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ESafe%3A%20A%20Memoir%20of%20Fatherhood%2C%20Foster%20Care%2C%20and%20the%20Risks%20We%20Take%20for%20Family%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%20(Atria%20Books%2C%20January%2030%2C%202024).%20Reprinted%20with%20permission%20from%20Atria%20Books.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgive-foster-child-safe-space-cope-emotional-trauma-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706618461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657376b57a3c8094d5db40f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgive-foster-child-safe-space-cope-emotional-trauma-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20my%20foster%20child%20had%20a%20tantrum%2C%20I%20realized%20the%20importance%20of%20providing%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20big%20feelings%20when%20he%20was%20experiencing%20trauma%20so%20he%20knew%20he%20was%20loved.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mark%20Daley%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgive-foster-child-safe-space-cope-emotional-trauma-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japanese%20Director%20Urara%20Matsubayashi%20on%20Speaking%20Up%20About%20Sexual%20Assault%2C%20Gender%20Gap%3A%20%E2%80%98%23MeToo%20Is%20Not%20Restricted%20to%20One%20Country%2C%20but%20the%20Entire%20World%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706618449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FUrara-Matsubayashi.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235891433%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20it%20is%20fa