.com%2Fpolitics%2Farchive%2F2023%2F11%2Fpeter-thiel-2024-election-politics-investing-life-views%2F675946%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20The%20Atlantic%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20that%20he%20was%20considering%20getting%20into%20nicotine%20patches%2C%20a%20therapy%20typically%20used%20to%20ween%20people%20off%20of%20smoking%2C%20because%20the%20drug%20may%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Breally%20good%20nootropic%20drug%20that%20raises%20your%20IQ%2010%20points.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECome%20and%20take%20it%2C%20Chuck.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Feh2mESetFL%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Feh2mESetFL%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0vOGqHev4K%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F0vOGqHev4K%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Senator%20Thom%20Tillis%20(%40SenThomTillis)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenThomTillis%2Fstatus%2F1749919489922093216%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20the%20outrage%20is%20all%20coming%20from%20this%20particular%20subset%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20members%20of%20Congress.%20Burchett%2C%20for%20example%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20%26quot%3Bhad%20to%20Google%20it%20to%20find%20out%20what%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%20Sen.%20JD%20Vance%20of%20Ohio%2C%20the%20youngest%20GOP%20member%20of%20the%20chamber%20and%20one%20who%20acknowledges%20being%20%26quot%3Bplugged%20into%20a%20lot%20of%20weird%20right-wing%20subcultures%2C%26quot%3B%20also%20indicated%20little%20knowledge%20of%20the%20right-wing%20hankering%20for%20nicotine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Senate%20office%20probably%20has%20the%20highest%20ratio%20of%20smokers%20of%20anybody%20in%20the%20US%20Senate%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20offered.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there's%20probably%20something%20to%20be%20said%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20the%20Zyn%20craze%20is%20most%20visible%20among%20younger%2C%20more%20online%2C%20and%20predominantly%20male%20conservatives%2C%20including%20those%20who%20staff%20GOP%20congressional%20offices%20and%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'pro-society'%20drug%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20variety%20of%20factors%20drive%20the%20proliferation%20of%20nicotine%20among%20the%20younger%20right-wing%20crowd.%20Demographically%20speaking%2C%20many%20young%20professional%20Republicans%20come%20from%20fraternity%20houses%2C%20sports%20teams%2C%20or%20other%20contexts%20where%20nicotine%20use%20is%20common.%20It's%20also%20the%20case%20that%20Capitol%20Hill%20and%20campaigns%20tend%20to%20be%20high-pressure%20environments%20where%20consumption%20of%20caffeine%20and%20alcohol%20is%20known%20to%20be%20rampant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Containers%20of%20%26quot%3BZyn%26quot%3B%20nicotine%20pouches.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b822a043bb77284ba1856e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EContainers%20of%20%26quot%3BZyn%26quot%3B%20nicotine%20pouches.%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20about%20everyone%20agrees%20that%20Carlson%20has%20been%20a%20singular%20force%20in%20mainstreaming%20Zyn%2C%20the%20Swedish-developed%20brand%20of%20nicotine%20pouches%20that%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC9667333%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eexploded%20in%20popularity%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20last%20several%20years%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZyn%20is%20pretty%20popular%20at%20least%20among%20Republican%20staff%20and%20seemingly%20some%20members%2C%20and%20Tucker%20Carlson's%20use%20of%20it%20no%20doubt%20popularized%20it%20on%20the%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20GOP%20Hill%20staffer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20these%20young%20conservatives%2C%20nicotine%20isn't%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20habit%20or%20recreation%20(though%20that's%20certainly%20part%20of%20it)%3A%20It's%20often%20seen%20as%20a%20way%20to%20boost%20productivity%2C%20whether%20it's%20via%20pouches%2C%20vaping%2C%20or%20gum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20use%20it%20whenever%20I%20write%20material%20for%20my%20show%2C%20or%20right%20before%20I%20go%20on%20the%20air%2C%20or%20if%20I%20ever%20have%20to%20do%20a%20big%20podcast%20appearance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Saagar%20Enjeti%2C%20the%20cohost%20of%20the%20anti-establishment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2Fbreakingpoints%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBreaking%20Points%26quot%3B%20YouTube%20show%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20I%20use%20to%20enhance%20my%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20gets%20the%20creative%20juices%20flowing%20during%20the%20day%20when%20I'm%20working%20and%20shitposting%20and%20whatnot%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Greg%20Price%2C%20the%20communications%20director%20for%20the%20State%20Freedom%20Caucus%20Network%20and%20frequent%20viral%20clip-cutter%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20tobacco%2C%20the%20science%20clearly%20shows%20that%20it%20causes%20cancer.%20But%20there%20hasn't%20been%20as%20much%20definitive%20research%20into%20the%20effects%20of%20non-tobacco%20nicotine%20on%20the%20body.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20that%2C%20many%20on%20the%20pro-nicotine%20right%20look%20toward%20Andrew%20Huberman%2C%20a%20neuroscience%20professor%20at%20Stanford%20University%2C%20and%20Dr.%20Peter%20Attia.%20Both%20men%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeterattiamd.com%2Fpodcast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epodcasts%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20have%20extolled%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuXs-zPc63kM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epotential%20benefits%20of%20nicotine%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20mind%20while%20also%20warning%20of%20its%20addictive%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20stimulant%2C%20it's%20not%20hard%20to%20see%20how%20nicotine%20could%20be%20a%20potential%20cognitive%20enhancer.%20But%20claims%20that%20the%20drug%20boosts%20testosterone%20rest%20on%20a%20shakier%20foundation%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fsmoking%2Fnicotine-and-testosterone%23nicotines-effect%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estudies%20showing%20mixed%20results.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20scientific%20evidence%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alzdiscovery.org%2Fuploads%2Fcognitive_vitality_media%2FNicotine-Cognitive-Vitality-For-Researchers.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAlzheimer's%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Parkinson's%20is%20similarly%20weak.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20nicotine%20use%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4958544%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elinked%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'They%20hate%20nicotine.%20They%20love%20THC'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20darker%20layer%20in%20all%20of%20this%20is%20a%20Carlson-inspired%20critique%20of%20the%20left's%20approach%20to%20drug%20regulation%20writ%20large%2C%20including%20the%20fentanyl%20crisis%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20ongoing%20push%20to%20legalize%20marijuana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20hate%20nicotine.%20They%20love%20THC%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlson%20said%20in%20a%20now-infamous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedailybeast.com%2Ftucker-carlson-nicotine-frees-your-mind%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emonologue%20on%20his%20Fox%20News%20show%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20main%20psychoactive%20component%20in%20marijuana.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20promoting%20weed%20to%20your%20children%20but%20they're%20not%20letting%20you%20use%20tobacco%20or%20even%20non-tobacco%20nicotine%20delivery%20devices%20which%20don't%20cause%20cancer.%20Why%20do%20they%20hate%20nicotine%3F%20Because%20nicotine%20frees%20your%20mind%2C%20and%20THC%20makes%20you%20compliant%20and%20passive.%20That's%20why.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20take%20a%20similar%2C%20though%20less%20conspiratorial%20approach%20to%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNicotine%2C%20when%20disaggregated%20from%20cigarettes%2C%20is%20a%20pro-society%20drug%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Enjeti.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20currently%20a%20major%20institutional-left%20push%20to%20legalize%20drugs%20I%20would%20call%20anti-society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnjeti%20also%20made%20something%20of%20a%20traditionalist%20argument%2C%20noting%20that%20high%20nicotine%20use%20correlated%20with%20a%20time%20that%20many%20consider%20to%20be%20a%20golden%20age%20in%20American%20innovation%20and%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20people%20that%20we%20respect%20most%2C%20including%20great%20thinkers%2C%20builders%2C%20and%20others%20who%20advanced%20society%20and%20really%20made%20us%20a%20great%20country%2C%20were%20all%20prolific%20nicotine%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Enjeti.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20all%20decided%20to%20shut%20that%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fr7t_GYRp-_4%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Tucker%20Carlson%3A%20Nicotine%20frees%20your%20mind%2C%20marij