20a%20PLA%20soldier%20in%20Tibetan%20language%2C%20as%20the%20siren%20of%20one%20of%20the%20PLA%20armoured%20vehicles%20blares%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20ancestral%20land.%20We%20graze%20our%20livestock%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%209-minute%2C%2050-second%20video%20shows%20the%20PLA%20soldiers%20and%20the%20herders%20getting%20into%20a%20heated%20argument%20as%20they%20come%20face%20to%20face.%20The%20video%20shows%20one%20batch%20of%20Chinese%20soldiers%2C%20led%20by%20an%20armoured%20vehicle%2C%20pushing%20the%20herders%20and%20their%20livestock%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20PLA%20soldier%20can%20also%20be%20seen%20blocking%20the%20camera%20lens%20of%20the%20herder%2C%20who%20is%20shooting%20the%20incident%2C%20even%20as%20his%20fellow%20soldiers%20around%20him%20continue%20to%20film%20the%20incident%20while%20waving%20at%20the%20herders%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20a%20visibly-agitated%20herder%2C%20who%20breaks%20from%20the%20scene%2C%20pulls%20out%20a%20sling%20from%20beneath%20his%20coat%2C%20puts%20a%20stone%20in%20it%20and%20swings%20it%20at%20the%20incoming%20armoured%20vehicle%2C%20which%20visibly%20escaped%20the%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20Leh%20Santosh%20Sukhadeva%20and%20SSP%20Leh%20for%20their%20comment%20about%20the%20development.%20This%20article%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChushul%20Councillor%20Konchok%20Stanzin%2C%20who%20posted%20the%20video%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20said%20that%20nomads%20put%20up%20a%20brave%20face%20when%20the%20PLA%20soldiers%20stopped%20their%20livestock%20from%20grazing.%20%E2%80%9CLivelihoods%20of%20locals%20have%20been%20taken%20away%20in%20the%20name%20of%20buffer%20zones%20and%20patrolling%20points.%20Our%20nomads%20are%20struggling%20for%20their%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20Stanzin%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20clash%2C%20the%20herders%20were%20forced%20to%20move%20out%20of%20the%20area%2C%20sparking%20anger%20in%20the%20nomadic%20community%20who%20depend%20on%20the%20pastures%20in%20the%20highlands%20of%20Ladakh%20for%20their%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Chinese%20soldiers%20have%20turned%20away%20nomads%20from%20their%20traditional%20lands%20in%20Ladakh.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20reports%20of%20incursion%20by%20China%20with%20Indian%20patrols%20also%20reportedly%20losing%20access%20to%20the%20strategic%20Depsang%20Plains%2C%20Demchok%20and%20other%20areas%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20of%20covering%20up%20%E2%80%9Cterritorial%20setbacks%E2%80%9D%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20while%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20denied%20the%20charges%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20landmark%20built%20by%20the%20Indian%20Army%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Rezang%20La%20battle%20of%20the%201962%20Sino-India%20conflict%20in%20Ladakh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Frezang-la-battle-landmark-removed-as-part-of-disengagement-councillor-says%5C%22%3Ewas%20dismantled%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20the%20disengagement%20process%20with%20China%2C%20prompting%20anger%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20and%20military%20level%20talks%20on%20the%20border%20dispute%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20failed%20to%20make%20any%20significant%20headway%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20South%20Asian%20giants%20has%20soured%20over%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20growing%20camaraderie%20with%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20clashes%20which%20brought%20the%20two%20South%20Asian%20giants%20on%20th