Fsecurity%2Fladakh-local-herders-clash-with-chinese-solders-over-access-to-grazing-land%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Return-to-office%20mandates%20aren't%20making%20companies%20more%20valuable%20and%20productive%2C%20study%20finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22worker%20with%20mask%20commuting%20into%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b7d8ec43bb77284ba1534c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHalfpoint%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EReturn-to-office%20mandates%20are%20often%20not%20succeeding%20in%20making%20companies%20more%20profitable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20according%20to%20a%20new%20paper%20that%20looks%20at%20how%20RTO%20mandates%20impact%20productivity%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20RTO%20mandates%20are%20hard%20to%20enforce%2C%20they%20probably%20don't%20make%20sense%20for%20that%20workplace.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EReturn-to-office%20mandates%20may%20not%20be%20doing%20what%20bosses%20want%20them%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4675401%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20researchers%20at%20the%20Katz%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Business%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pittsburgh%20examines%20whether%20pushing%20employees%20into%20the%20office%20increases%20productivity%20and%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BResults%20of%20our%20determinant%20analyses%20are%20consistent%20with%20managers%20using%20RTO%20mandates%20to%20reassert%20control%20over%20employees%20and%20blame%20employees%20as%20a%20scapegoat%20for%20bad%20firm%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20authors%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20our%20findings%20do%20not%20support%20the%20argument%20that%20managers%20impose%20mandates%20because%20they%20believe%20RTO%20increases%20firm%20values.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20analyzed%20public%20RTO%20data%20from%20137%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20firms%20and%20determined%20that%20RTO%20mandates%20were%20more%20common%20for%20firms%20that%20had%20poor%20prior%20stock%20market%20performance.%20RTO%20mandates%20were%20more%20common%20for%20firms%20with%20%26quot%3Bmale%20and%20powerful%20CEOs.%26quot%3B%20The%20authors%20found%20no%20significant%20impact%20of%20RTO%20mandates%20on%20stock%20returns%20or%20firm%20profitability.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20researchers%20noted%20that%20their%20data%20often%20didn't%20specify%20how%20many%20days%20back%20in%20the%20office%20were%20required%20by%20the%20companies%2C%20meaning%20there%20could%20be%20differences%20in%20performance%20between%20full-time%20and%20part-time%20RTO%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20using%20employee%20job%20satisfaction%20data%20from%20Glassdoor%2C%20the%20researchers%20found%20that%20RTO%20mandates%20reduced%20workers'%20ratings%20for%20work-life%20balance%2C%20senior%20management%2C%20and%20job%20satisfaction.%20Still%2C%20many%20employees%20may%20agree%20with%20RTO%20decisions%20as%20a%20way%20to%20increase%20collaboration%20and%20better%20separate%20work%20from%20home%2C%20the%20researchers%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERTO%20mandates%20have%20divided%20many%20offices%20nationwide%2C%20including%20at%20leading%20tech%20and%20financial%20companies.%20In%202023%2C%20over%205%2C000%20Amazon%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-return-to-office-policy-petition-30000-staff-remote-work-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigned%20a%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20company's%20return-to-office%20mandate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-hr-chief-rejects-petition-against-return-to-office-policy-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20Amazon%20rejected%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%202%2C300%20Disney%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-employees-petition-against-working-four-days-in-office-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ealso%20signed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20petition%20against%20the%20company's%20four-day%20in-person%20workweek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20workers%20are%20more%20productive%20remotely%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20argument%20for%20%E2%80%94%20or%20against%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0bringing%20employees%20back%20into%20the%20office.%20Some%20early%20research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwfh-work-from-home-decreases-productivity-18-percent-study-rto-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehas%20suggested%20that%20remote%20workers%20are%20less%20productive%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-innovation-collaboration-return-to-office-work-from-home-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elogging%20in%20from%20home%20curbs%20innovation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frbsf.org%2Feconomic-research%2Fpublications%2Feconomic-letter%2F2024%2Fjanuary%2Fdoes-working-from-home-boost-productivity-growth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erecent%20analysis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20San%20Francisco%20finds%20that%20shifting%20to%20remote%20work%2C%20%26quot%3Bon%20its%20own%2C%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20a%20major%20factor%20explaining%20differences%20across%20sectors%20in%20productivity%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20RTO%20mandates%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20these%20are%20hard%20to%20enforce%20then%20they%20likely%20do%20not%20make%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20Nick%20Bloom%2C%20a%20Stanford%20economist%20and%20work-from-home%20researcher%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%20%26quot%3BA%20well-executed%20RTO%20will%20have%20employees%20back%20in%20the%20office%20for%20maybe%202%20or%203%20days%20a%20week%20when%20all%20employees%20are%20back%20on%20the%20same%20days%2C%20they%20are%20working%20together%20connecting%2C%20with%20energy%20in%20the%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20an%20RTO%20mandate%20is%20well%20done%20is%20to%20make%20managers%20have%20%26quot%3Bsome%20explicit%20part%20of%20their%20evaluation%20focused%20on%20mentoring%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20Bloom.%20That%20incentivizes%20leaders%20to%20figure%20out%20what's%20the%20best%20way%20to%20mentor%20and%20develop%20their%20teams%2C%20often%20one%20of%20the%20goals%20of%20a%20return%20to%20office%20proclamation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBadly%20run%20RTO%20will%20be%20requiring%20minimum%20days%20per%20week%20but%20with%20no%20guidance%20on%20days%2C%20and%20no%20guidance%20on%20activities%20in%20the%20office.%20Then%20folks%20come%20in%20just%20to%20continue%20on%20zoom%20calls%20all%20day%2C%20or%20badge%20swipe%20to%20get%20coffee%20and%20leave%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20CEOs%20seem%20to%20have%20put%20the%20brakes%20on%20fully%20yanking%20workers%20back%20in.%20Just%204%25%20of%20American%20CEOs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.conference-board.org%2Fpublications%2FC-Suite-Outlook-2024-leading-for-tomorrow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurveyed%20by%20The%20Conference%20Board%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20they'd%20prioritize%20bringing%20workers%20back%20into%20the%20office%20full-time%20this%20year%2C%20while%2027%25%20said%20that%20maintaining%20hybrid%20work%20was%20a%20human%20capital%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20are%20in%20any%20type%20of%20manager%20or%20leadership%20role%2C%20if%20they%20have%20to%20see%20people%2C%20if%20they%20have%20to%20see%20butts%20in%20seats%20to%20think%20people%20are%20working%2C%20they%20don't%20know%20how%20people%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Danielle%2C%20a%20millennial%20manager%20who%20quit%20her%20job%20over%20an%20RTO%20push%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanager-quit-over-rto-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIs%20return-to-office%20not%20working%20for%20you%20or%20your%20company%3F%20Contact%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajkaplan%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejkaplan%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ansheidlower%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ensheidlower%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-mandates-remote-work-stock-returns-productivity-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706612762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b7d93143bb77284ba15374%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-mandates-remote-work-stock-returns-productivity-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bosses%20say%20they%20want%20workers%20in%20because%20it'll%20make%20the%20company%20more%20valuable.%20A%20new%20study%20suggests%20that's%20not%20true.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan%2CNoah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-mandates-remote-work-stock-returns-productivity-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20I.N.D.I.A.%20Alliance%20Looks%20Like%202019's%20UPA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20is%20facing%20internal%20turmoil%2C%20gradually%20unraveling.%20TMC%20leader%20and%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20adopted%20an%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bekla%20chalo%20re%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Eapproach%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20distancing%20herself%20from%20the%20alliance.%20The%20AAP%20has%20decided%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20Punjab%2C%20ending%20months%20of%20indecisive%20dialogue%20with%20the%20Congress.%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20once%20a%20strong%20contender%20for%20the%20position%20of%20I.N.D.I.A.%20Convenor%2C%20has%20gone%20back%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%20yet%20again.%20Even%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20is%20demanding%2023%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20despite%20facing%20a%20split%20within%20its%20ranks.%20Meanwhile%2C%20talks%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20have%20hit%20some%20sort%20roadblock%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20demanding%2020%20seats%20while%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20offered%2011%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20developments%20will%20likely%20impact%20the%20outcome%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Punjab%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20UP%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20the%20opposition's%20hopes%20were%20pinned%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20share%20and%20its%20tally%20of%20303%20seats.%20These%20states%20collectively%20account%20for%20223%20seats%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20having%20won%20more%20than%20half%20(122)%20in%202019%2C%20constituting%2041%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha's%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%2C%20which%20initially%20agreed%20to%20concede%20only%202%20out%20of%2042%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20contest%20all%2042%20seats%20independently.%20Had%20Congress%20and%20TMC%20formed%20an%20alliance%20in%202019%2C%20TMC%20might%20have%20secured%206%20more%20seats%20than%20its%20actual%20tally%20of%2022%2C%20and%20the%20BJP's%20count%20would%20have%20been%20reduced%20by%206%20seats.%20This%20shift%20is%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20will%20likely%20contest%20on%2013%20seats.%20Any%20alliance%20was%20never%20on%20the%20table%20here%2C%20given%20that%20the%20AAP%20had%20defeated%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%202022%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20its%20vote%20share%20is%20anti-Congress.%20Had%20they%20joined%20forces%2C%20it%20could%20have%20pushed%20anti-Congress%20voters%20towards%20the%20Akalis%20or%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20abandoned%20the%20RJD-Left-Congress%20alliance%20to%20rejoin%20the%20NDA.%20This%20move%20strengthens%20the%20NDA's%20position%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20it%20swept%20in%202019%20by%20winning%2039%20of%20the%2040%20seats.%20Without%20Nitish%2C%20the%20NDA's%20tally%20would%20have%20likely%20dwindled%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20combined%20opposition%20consisting%20of%20JDU%2C%20RJD%2C%20INC%2C%20and%20Left%20Parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Congress%20contested%2025%20seats%2C%20and%20the%20NCP%20contested%2019%2C%20leaving%204%20seats%20for%20smaller%20parties.%20However%2C%20complications%20have%20arisen%20with%20the%20involvement%20of%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20in%20seat-sharing%20negotiations.%20With%2013%20of%20its%2018%20MPs%20now%20under%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20leadership%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20Uddhav%20faction's%20status%20has%20diminished.%20Despite%20this%2C%20it%20is%20demanding%2023%20seats%2C%20the%20same%20number%20it%20used%20to%20contest%20with%20the%20BJP%20as%20part%20of%20an%20alliance.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20NCP%20has%20experienced%20a%20split%2C%20increasing%20the%20Congress%20party's%20bargaining%20power%20within%20the%20MVA%20in%20the%20state%2C%20though%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Uddhav%20Sena%20faction%20have%20yielded%20very%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20UP%2C%20the%20SP%20has%20allotted%207%20seats%20to%20the%20RLD%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20is%20demanding%2020%20seats.%20In%202014%2C%20when%20all%20opposition%20parties%20contested%20separately.%20The%20Congress%20won%202%20seats%20and%20was%20the%20runner-up%20in%206%2C%20indicating%20its%20standalone%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%2C%20formed%20with%20much%20fanfare%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20saw%2026%20opposition%20parties%20unite%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20upcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20UPA%20was%20rebranded%20as%20I.N.D.I.A.%20in%20the%20July%20meeting%20of%20opposition%20parties.%20The%20UPA%20originally%20included%20parties%20like%20the%20RJD%2C%20DMK%2C%20JMM%2C%20NCP%2C%20and%20the%20IUML.%20It%20gained%20strength%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20JD(U)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20faction)%2C%20TMC%2C%20SP%2C%20and%20the%20AAP%2C%20broadening%20its%20base%20and%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20generated%20optimism%20among%20opposition%20supporters%2C%20with%20many%20commentators%20and%20experts%20predicting%20a%20strong%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20in%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%20scheduled%20for%20April-May.%20The%20alliance%20garnered%20media%20attention%20and%20seemed%20to%20set%20the%20agenda%20in%20the%20initial%20months%2C%20up%20until%20mid-September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Congress%20shifted%20its%20focus%20to%20state%20elections%20after%20the%20initial%20trends%20suggested%20it%20might%20win%20three%20out%20of%20the%20five%20states.%20This%20gave%20the%20Congress%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20confidence%2C%20and%20it%20hoped%20to%20leverage%20these%20victories%20as%20a%20bargaining%20chip%20against%20regional%20parties.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20election%20results%20came%20in%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20winning%20just%20one%20state%2C%20Telangana%2C%20out%20of%20the%20five%2C%20it%20backtracked.%20By%20then%2C%20the%20allies%20were%20growing%20increasingly%20discontent%20with%20Congress's%20attitude%2C%20sowing%20the%20seeds%20of%20discord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20contested%20422%20seats.%20Regional%20forces%2C%20including%20the%20TMC%2C%20had%20requested%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20to%20contest%20300%20seats%2C%20meaning%20they%20wanted%20the%20Congress%20to%20contest%20fewer%20seats%20in%20UP%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20among%20others.%20With%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab%20now%20out%20of%20consideration%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20UP.%20If%20an%20alliance%20there%20does%20not%20materialize%2C%20which%20seems%20likely%20at%20this%20point%2C%20the%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20may%20effectively%20become%20defunct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20the%20alliance%20would%20revert%20to%20the%20old%20UPA%2C%20which%20was%20already%20in%20place%20in%202019%20in%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20accounting%20for%20just%20161%20seats%20(30%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha's%20strength).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20currently%20appears%20to%20be%20in%20complete%20disarray%2C%20and%20with%20the%20highly%20charged%20emotional%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20country%20following%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20hold%20a%20significant%20advantage%20at%20this%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706612760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fj5iaj1lg_opposition-bengaluru-pti_625x300_18_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Findia-alliance-looks-like-2019s-upa-4671806%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20I.N.D.I.A.%20bloc%20curr