%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20noted%20that%20conspiracy%20to%20murder%20Mahatama%20Gandhi%20did%20exist.%20Apte%20and%20Nathuram%20Godse%20remained%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchief%20organisers%E2%80%9D%20throughout%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Achhru%20Ram%20and%20Justice%20Bhandari%20recommended%20the%20commutation%20of%20sentence%20of%20Gopal%20Godse%20and%20Madanlal%20Pahwa%20owing%20to%20their%20young%20age%2C%20but%20Justice%20Khosla%20disagreed%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20Justice%20Achhru%20Ram%20to%20commute%20the%20sentence%20of%20Madanlal%20Pahwa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Achhru%20Ram%20observed%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20are%20quite%20young%20and%20in%20the%20bloom%20of%20their%20lives.%20Both%20seemed%20to%20have%20succumbed%20to%20influences%20exercised%20over%20them%20by%20stronger%20and%20more%20determined%20persons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khosla%20in%20his%20one%20paragraph%20judgement%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EI%20wish%2C%20however%2C%20to%20disassociate%20myself%20from%20the%20recommendation%20for%20mercy%20made%20by%20my%20Learned%20Brother%20Achhru%20Ram%20J.%20in%20favour%20of%20Madanlal%20Pahwa.%20Pahwa%20took%20a%20very%20prominent%20part%20in%20the%20plan%20of%20conspiracy%20originally%20conceived.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Bhandari%20noted%20that%20the%20observations%20of%20the%20Special%20Judge%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20was%20unwarranted%20and%20that%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20impossible%20for%20any%20police%20officer%2C%20however%20capable%20and%20efficient%20he%20might%20have%20been%2C%20to%20have%20prevented%20Nathuram%20from%20committing%20the%20crime%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20slackness%20on%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20Justice%20Bhandari%20observed%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20evidence%20on%20record%20satisfies%20me%20(a)%20that%20no%20opportunity%20was%20afforded%20to%20the%20police%20to%20explain%20the%20circumstances%20which%20prevented%20them%20from%20apprehending%20Nathuram%20before%20the%2030th%20January%20and%20thereby%20saving%20the%20life%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%3B%20(b)%20that%20Madanlal%20failed%20to%20supply%20the%20names%20of%20the%20conspirators%20to%20the%20police%3B%20(c)%20that%20even%20if%20those%20names%20were%20supplied%20it%20was%20extremely%20difficult%2C%20if%20not%20impossible%2C%20for%20the%20police%20to%20arrest%20Nathuram%20who%20was%20going%20about%20from%20place%20to%20place%20under%20assumed%20names%20and%20who%20was%20determined%20to%20assassinate%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20even%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20losing%20his%20own%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Justice%20Achhru%20Ram%3Cem%3E%C2%A0noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20concluding%201%20want%20to%20advert%20to%20some%20remarks%20made%20by%20the%20learned%20Special%20Judge%20as%20to%20the%20slackness%20shown%20in%20the%20investigation%20during%20the%20period%20between%20the%2020th%20and%20the%2030th%20January%201948%20but%20for%20which.%20in%20the%20view%20of%20the%20learned%20Judge%2C%20the%20tragedy%20could%20have%20been%20prevented.%20I%20must%20say%20that%20I%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20discover%20any%20justification%20at%20all%20for%20these%20remarks%20which%20in%20my%20judgment%20were%20wholly%20uncalled%20for.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Justice%20Khosla%3Cem%3E%C2%A0stated%20%E2%80%9CI%20concur%20with%20the%20conclusions%20arrived%20at%20by%20my%20learned%20brothers%20Bhandari%20and%20Achhru%20Ram%20JJ.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20petition%20for%20special%20leave%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20privy%20council%20was%20lodged%20by%20all%20the%20five%20who%20stood%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%20by%20the%20High%20court%20%E2%80%93%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20Apte%2C%20Karkare%2C%20Pahwa%20and%20Gopal%20Godse%20and%20the%20same%20was%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20almost%2075%20years%2C%20a%20petition%20was%20filed%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20April%202023%20alleging%20mistrial%20in%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20assassination%20case%20in%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bench%20comprising%20of%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul%20and%20Justice%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20imposed%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000%20on%20Abhinav%20Bharat%20Congress%E2%80%99%20while%20dismissing%20the%20petition%2C%20noted%20that%2C%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20most%20misconceived%20petition%20under%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20The%20parties%20cannot%20walk%20into%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20any%20pleading%20or%20with%20any%20prayer%20they%20want.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Farticles%2Fmahatma-gandhi-murder-case-brief-facts-247956%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20LiveLaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706612453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30091446%2FIMG_1737.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fkey-facts-on-the-mahatma-gandhi-assassination-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20timeline%20of%20the%20case%20and%20details%20of%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20courts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fkey-facts-on-the-mahatma-gandhi-assassination-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Install%20temple%20boards%20saying%20non-Hindus%20not%20allowed%3A%20Madras%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706612406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107262528%2Cimgsize-1629297.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Finstall-boards-in-all-temples-indicating-that-non-hindus-are-not-allowed-beyon