20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20was%20found%20guilty%2C%20the%20Spanish%20Defence%20Ministry%20wanted%20around%20%24103%2C000%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20scrambling%20the%20fighter%20jets%2C%20while%20he%20also%20faced%20a%20possible%20fine%20of%20around%20%2417%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20judge%20cleared%20Verma%20on%20Thursday%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20joke%20was%20made%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20strictly%20private%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20could%20not%20even%20remotely%20assume...%20that%20the%20joke%20he%20played%20on%20his%20friends%20could%20be%20intercepted%20or%20detected%20by%20the%20British%20services%2C%20nor%20by%20third%20parties%20other%20than%20his%20friends%20who%20received%20the%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20question%20left%20unanswered%20in%20the%20case%20was%20how%20the%20security%20services%20saw%20Verma's%20Snapchat%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20previously%20thought%20the%20WiFi%20network%20at%20London%20Gatwick%20Airport%20could%20have%20intercepted%20it%2C%20but%20an%20airport%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20BBC%20it%20doesn't%20have%20that%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspanish-judge-clears-british-teen-menorca-flight-bomb-hoax-charges-2024-01-25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20judge%20suggested%20one%20of%20Verma's%20friends%20in%20the%20Snapchat%20group%20could%20have%20told%20the%20police%20%E2%80%94%20but%20then%20that%20person%20would%20have%20to%20face%20the%20public-disorder%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassenger-avoids-120k-bill-after-bomb-joke-scrambled-fighter-jets-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706611800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F