p%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20he%20is%20committed%20to%20national%20gun%20safety.%20His%20administration%20has%20created%20a%20federal%20office%20dedicated%20to%20the%20cause%2C%20secured%20%24438%20million%20in%20grant%20funding%2C%20advocated%20for%20secure%20firearm%20storage%2C%20and%20invested%20in%20community%20crisis%20response%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20continued%20federal%20action%20hangs%20on%20whether%20Congress%20passes%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F118th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F1699%3Fs%3D1%26r%3D29%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOffice%20of%20Gun%20Violence%20Prevention%20Act%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20cement%20an%20office%20of%20gun%20violence%20prevention%20in%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department.%20The%20bill%20was%20first%20introduced%20last%20spring%20and%20has%20not%20yet%20become%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20fails%20to%20move%20forward%2C%20the%20next%20president%20could%20disband%20many%20current%20efforts%20toward%20gun%20violence%20prevention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20and%20Nikki%20Haley%20%E2%80%94%20the%20two%20leading%20candidates%20for%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%20%E2%80%94%20have%20signaled%20that%20they%20support%20the%20Second%20Amendment%20and%20will%20not%20tighten%20gun%20restrictions%20if%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGun%20violence%20will%20be%20a%20major%20issue%20for%20young%20voters%20in%20November%2C%20per%20reports%20from%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fofficial-polls%2Ffox-news-poll-voters-favor-gun-limits-arming-citizens-reduce-gun-violence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D3025870bb80ed062a39170b8abed6c19845f19a2083988480c55bd63bbcdaab0%26postID%3D65b41d1285420bcd666648d8%26postSlug%3Dbiden-trump-gun-violence-prevention-congress-budget-election-2024-1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.scribd.com%252Fdocument%252F674304056%252FGuns-and-Voting%2B%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrennan%20Center%20for%20Justice.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20As%20election%20season%20gears%20up%2C%20gu%3C%2Fstrong%3En-related%20injuries%20have%20surpassed%20car%20crashes%20as%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20young%20people%2C%20and%2018%2C874%20Americans%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20gun%20violence%20last%20year%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gunviolencearchive.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGun%20Violence%20Archive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBreaking%20down%20Biden's%20investment%20in%20gun%20violence%20prevention%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20almost%20six%20months%20since%20The%20Biden-Harris%20Administration%20created%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fogvp%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWhite%20House%20Office%20of%20Gun%20Violence%20Prevention%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tasked%20with%20reducing%20gun%20violence%20across%20the%20country%20through%20executive%20and%20legislative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20public%20statement%2C%20The%20White%20House%20said%20Biden%20is%20%26quot%3Btaking%20more%20meaningful%20executive%20action%20than%20any%20other%20president%20to%20make%20our%20schools%2C%20churches%2C%20grocery%20stores%2C%20and%20communities%20safer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20Biden%20signed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhats-in-new-bipartisan-senate-gun-bill-legislative-text-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBipartisan%20Safer%20Communities%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022.%20The%20law%20%E2%80%94%20backed%20by%20many%20key%20Democratic%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhere-are-15-republican-senators-backing-senate-gun-bill-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublican%20lawmakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20supports%20state-level%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-house-republican-vote-for-a-nationwide-red-flag-law-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ered%20flag%26quot%3B%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20enhances%20school%20security%20programs%2C%20expands%20access%20to%20crisis%20mental%20health%20services%2C%20and%20aims%20to%20reduce%20gun-involved%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20said%20he%20is%20calling%20on%20Congress%20to%20ban%20assault%20weapons%20and%20high-capacity%20magazines%2C%20require%20background%20checks%20for%20all%20gun%20sales%2C%20and%20mandate%20the%20safe%20storage%20of%20firearms.%20The%20administration%20has%20also%20taken%20action%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FOGVP-Safer-States-Policy-Agenda.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20support%20states%20in%20passing%20gun%20safety%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGun%20violence%20is%20a%20nationwide%20problem%20that%20requires%20a%20nationwide%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20federal%20and%20state%20working%20hand-in-hand%20to%20keep%20guns%20away%20from%20people%20who%20have%20no%20business%20being%20armed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Feinblatt%2C%20president%20of%20the%20nonpartisan%20organization%20Everytown%20for%20Gun%20Safety%20said%20in%20a%20December%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden's%20strategy%20framework%20is%20outlined%20in%20his%20%26quot%3BSafer%20America%20Plan.%26quot%3B%20The%20plan%20has%20seen%20support%20across%20the%20aisle%2C%20especially%20for%20its%20proposed%20investment%20in%20responsible%20gun%20ownership%20and%20promise%20to%20hold%20gun%20manufacturers%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20prevention%20strategies%20have%20seen%20results%20%E2%80%94%20as%20of%20January%2C%20the%20Justice%20Department%20has%20denied%20more%20than%20500%20illegal%20gun%20purchases%20by%20people%20under%2021%20years%20old.%20Annual%20gun%20deaths%20and%20gun%20sales%20have%20declined%20slightly%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden's%20plan%20also%20invested%20in%20crime%20reduction%20by%20adding%20%26quot%3Bmore%20police%20officers%20on%20our%20streets%20for%20accountable%2C%20community%20policing.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20adding%20police%20department%20resources%20has%20been%20met%20with%20concern%20from%20some%20civil%20rights%20and%20advocacy%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20are%20pleased%20with%20the%20president's%20commitment%20to%20investing%20in%20communities%2C%20we%20strongly%20urge%20him%20not%20to%20repeat%20the%20grave%20errors%20of%20the%201990s%20%E2%80%94%20policies%20that%20exacerbated%20racial%20disparities%2C%20contributed%20to%20widespread%20police%20abuses%2C%20and%20created%20our%20current%20crisis%20of%20mass%20incarceration%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20American%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20said%20in%20a%20public%20statement%20about%20the%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bipartisan%20Safer%20Communities%20Act%20has%20made%20%24250%20million%20in%20grant%20funding%20available%20to%20community-based%20organizations%20working%20to%20reduce%20gun%20violence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetrace.org%2F2023%2F12%2Fdata-gun-violence-deaths-america%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Trace%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20far%2C%20over%20%24200%20million%20of%20that%20money%20has%20been%20awarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20additional%20%24238%20million%20dollars%20provided%20under%20the%20act%20will%20be%20used%20for%20legislation%20aimed%20at%20disarming%20dangerous%20people%2C%20mental%20health%20resources%2C%20and%20other%20crisis%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20also%20set%20aside%20%24750%20million%20to%20be%20used%20to%20implement%20red-flag%20and%20crisis%20intervention%20laws%20in%20individual%20states%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20new%20laws%20or%20budget%20allocations%20toward%20gun%20violence%20prevention%20must%20also%20be%20approved%20by%20both%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20and%20the%20Senate.%20And%20although%20the%20president%20can%20make%20Executive%20Orders%2C%20laws%20on%20gun%20rights%20and%20gun%20access%20can%20only%20be%20passed%20by%20Congress%20or%20at%20the%20state%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20Office%20of%20Gun%20Violence%20Prevention%2C%20specifically%2C%20is%20funded%20through%20Congress'%20annual%20executive%20office%20appropriations.%20Spending%20for%20the%20office%20is%20at%20the%20discretion%20of%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-gun-violence-prevention-congress-budget-election-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706611681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b41ecef4b446f3be9d64fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-gun-violence-prevention-congress-budget-election-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Biden%20has%20poured%20resources%20into%20gun%20violence%20prevention%2C%20but%20the%20election%20will%20determine%20if%20the%20initiatives%20continue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40insider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-gun-violence-prevention-congress-budget-election-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Freedom%20Was%20Won%2C%20Yes%2C%20But%20it%20Was%20Written%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162100%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESulekha%20Ink%20is%20the%20brand%20after%20which%20I%20was%20named%20%E2%80%98Sreelekha%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pre-independence%20Swadeshi%20ink%20conceived%20by%20my%20grandfather%20whom%20we%20fondly%20called%20Nani%20Dadu%20(Nani%20Gopal%20Maitra)%20from%20Rajshahi%20in%201934.%20The%20place%2C%20now%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20is%20where%20I%20would%20have%20been%20likely%20to%20be%20born%20if%20India%20was%20not%20partitioned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20story%20goes%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20Gandhiji%20%E2%80%93%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20tough%20situation%20of%20not%20having%20an%20indigenous%20ink%20to%20sign%20freedom%20petitions.%20All%20inks%20were%20manufactured%20overseas%20and%20Gandhiji%20refused%20to%20sign%20using%20any%20of%20them.%20It%20was%20at%20that%20point%20two%20brothers%20from%20Rajshahi%20took%20up%20the%20challenge.%20Nani%20Gopal%20and%20Shankacharya%20Maitra%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20homegrown%20ink%20to%20match%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20vision.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20this%20is%20the%20ink%20that%20was%20used%20to%20sign%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20in%201950.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20read%20of%20this%20creation%20story%20in%20my%20Thakuma%E2%80%99s%20(grandma%E2%80%99s)%20diaries.%20She%20was%20a%20diligent%20diary%20writer%20and%20the%20diary%20that%20I%20am%20currently%20reading%20dates%20back%20to%201952.%20Her%20writings%20cover%20incidents%20spanning%20the%20years%20around%201930%20to%201950.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20like%20entering%20a%20time%20machine.%20It%20was%20the%20thick%20of%20Swadeshi%20Movement%20that%20had%20encouraged%20the%20boycotting%20of%20foreign%20goods%20and%20the%20promotion%20of%20indigenous%20industries.%20It%20fostered%20nationalism%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhiji%20had%20addressed%20his%20followers%20regarding%20the%20boycott%20of%20foreign%20goods%20in%20everyday%20life.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20went%20much%20beyond%20salt%20and%20khadi%20and%20had%20pointedly%20spoken%20about%20ink.%20But%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ell%20inks%20were%20manufactured%20overseas%20and%20Gandhiji%20refused%20to%20sign%20using%20any%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu-300x203.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162121%2FNoni-Dadu-1024x694.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694940%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22732%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENoni%20Gopal%20Maitra%2C%20with%20others.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20Revolution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20time%20I%20read%20Thakuma%E2%80%99s%20writings%20on%20Gandhiji%2C%20I%20pinch%20myself.%20Is%20this%20the%20Gandhiji%20of%20history%20books%3F%20Before%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhiji%20was%20arrested%20in%201932%20by%20the%20Commissionerate%20of%20Bombay%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20taken%20to%20the%20Yerawada%20Central%20Jail%20in%20Pune%2C%20he%20had%20assigned%20Satish%20Chandra%20Dasgupta%2C%20chief%20chemist%20at%20Bengal%20Chemical%2C%20with%20the%20task%20of%20creating%20a%20homegrown%20ink.%20And%20Dasgupta%20in%20turn%20had%20Nani%20Gopal%20Maitra%20in%20mind.%20Nani%20Dadu%20was%20then%20a%20physics%20teacher%20at%20Rajshahi%20University%20and%20was%20running%20an%20underground%20Swadeshi%20chapter%20of%20the%20Rajshahi%20Mukti%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajshahi%20back%20then%20was%20a%20hub%20of%20education%2C%20trade%20and%20culture%20with%20a%20major%20focus%20on%20silk%20production.%20The%20British%20invariably%20had%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20prosperous%20zones%20and%20strategically%20established%20the%20Administrative%20District%20in%201772%20and%20The%20Rajshahi%20Municipal%20Corporation%20in%201876.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThakuma%E2%80%99s%20pages%20also%20mention%20that%20Gandhiji%20used%20reed%20pens%2C%20instead%20of%20foreign-made%20fountain%20pens%20and%20that%20he%20was%20a%20prolific%20writer.%20This%20is%20entirely%20believable%2C%20since%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20letter%20collection%20itself%20runs%20into%20thousands%20of%20pages.%20Influenced%20by%20this%2C%20Thakuma%2C%20too%2C%20tried%20writing%20her%20diary%20with%20a%20reed%20pen%20which%20resulted%20in%20illegible%20handwriting%20for%20quite%20a%20few%20pages!%20Evidently%20the%20Swadeshi%20movement%20was%20raging%20through%20her%20head%20and%20heart.%20And%20this%20was%20clear%20from%20her%20mentions%20of%20what%20she%20wore%20and%20what%20she%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20diary%2C%20she%20writes%20about%20Nani%20Dadu%20being%20released%20from%20the%20jail.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAj%20khushir%20din%20%3C%2Fem%3E(today%20is%20a%20happy%20day).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162131%2Fink-pot.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162131%2Fink-pot.jpg%20669w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162131%2Fink-pot-300x226.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694941%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESulekha%20Ink%20bottles.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20behind%20bars%20for%20taking%20part%20in%20%E2%80%98Satyagraha%20Andolan%E2%80%99%20the%20non-violence%20revolution%20started%20by%20Gandhiji.%20On%20being%20released%2C%20he%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Satish%20Chandra%20Dasgupta%20(then%20chief%20chemist%20of%20Bengal%20Chemical)%20to%20meet%20Gandhiji.%C2%A0%20And%20the%20seed%20of%20a%20swadeshi%20ink%20was%20planted%20in%20his%20head.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFreshly%20designated%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20creating%20a%20homegrown%20ink%2C%20my%20grandfather%20managed%20a%20makeshift%20laboratory%20in%20the%20Maitra%20residence%20in%20Rajshahi%20and%20spent%20hours%20creating%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20ink.%20This%20ink%20was%20to%20write%20the%20freedom%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20one%20of%20my%20earliest%20memories%2C%20I%20remember%20this%20scene%20being%20enacted%20to%20me%20by%20Nani%20Dadu.%20He%20would%20mimic%20tiptoeing%20down%20the%20stairs%20and%20entering%20his%20lab.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20when%20everybody%20was%20asleep%2C%20he%20would%20unbox%20his%20secret%20formula%2C%20and%20create%20a%20magic%20potion%20called%20ink.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20Thakuma%E2%80%99s%20diary%20says%20that%20it%20was%201934%20when%20the%20black%20ink%20was%20born%20at%20the%20Maitra%20residence%20in%20Rajshahi.%20The%20family%20had%20spent%20all%20their%20jewellery%20and%20savings%20to%20make%20this%20dream%20come%20true.%20By%20July%201934%2C%20a%20box%20of%20ink%20was%20ready%20to%20leave%20for%20Gandhiji%20to%20use.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20342px)%2085vw%2C%20342px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22342%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02.png%20894w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02-224x300.png%20224w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162359%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.02-763x1024.png%20763w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694944%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Sulekha%20Ink%20advertisement.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhen%20a%20big%20name%20gets%20to%20name%20it%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20story%20goes%2C%20on%20August%205%2C%201934%2C%20Gandhiji%20was%20in%20Wardha%20after%20completing%20his%20Harijan%20Tour.%20Jamnalal%20Bajaj%20had%20hosted%20him%20in%20his%20house%20where%20a%20box%20of%20ink%20arrived%20at%20the%20Bajaj%20residence.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Gandhiji%20inaugurated%20the%20ink%20by%20writing%20a%20note%20to%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20name%20it.%20And%20it%20was%20Tagore%20who%20named%20it%20Sulekha%2C%20a%20portmanteau%20for%20the%20Bengali%20phrase%20for%20%E2%80%98beautiful%20writing.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20moments%20in%20the%20diary%20are%20extraordinary.%20They%20are%20big%20as%20historical%20event%20and%20as%20a%20reader%2C%20it%20took%20me%20a%20while%20to%20let%20it%20sink%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20Thakuma%20telling%20me%20many%20times%20over%20that%20Rajshahi%20was%20synonymous%20with%20Sulekha.%20It%20is%20because%20of%20this%20that%20when%20the%20country%20was%20divided%20and%20we%20came%20to%20Calcutta%2C%20that%20a%20new%20name%20%E2%80%93%20not%20the%20same%20one%20%E2%80%93%20was%20given%20to%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20all%20of%20her%20diaries%20and%20there%20are%20indeed%20time%20lapses.%20But%20she%20does%20mention%20that%20Tagore%20dedicated%20Sulekha%20Ink%20to%20the%20nation%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20Indian%20independence.%20He%20himself%20was%20so%20charmed%20by%20the%20black%20ink%20that%20he%20used%20it%20to%20write%20some%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20literature%20of%20all%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20moment%20India%20was%20waiting%20for%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDiaries%20are%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20times.%20The%20pages%20talk%20about%20the%20legendary%20success%20of%20Sulekha%20over%20the%20decades%20and%20becoming%20a%20household%20name%20in%20Bengal.%20The%20Maitra%20brothers%20moved%20the%20ink%20manufacturing%20facility%20to%20Bowbazar%20in%20Calcutta%20in%201938.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20or%20more%20diaries%20later%2C%20I%20arrived%20at%20August%2014%2C%201947.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThakuma%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESwadhin%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eholam%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20We%20become%20independent.%20The%20bondage%20of%20colonial%20slavery%20was%20at%20last%20broken%2C%20and%20we%20were%20longer%20subjects%20of%20the%20Crown.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EForever%20etched%20in%20memory%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Nani%20Dadu%20and%20Thakuma%20have%20long%20left%20us.%20I%20moved%20to%20Bombay.%20But%20her%20diaries%20have%20found%20a%20new%20life%20with%20me.%20Who%20visited%20when%2C%20who%20stayed%20with%20us%2C%20what%20they%20ate%20that%20day%2C%20which%20doctor%20they%20went%20to%2C%20every%20detail%20was%20chalked%20down.%20But%20ever%20since%20I%20have%20been%20reading%20her%20diary%20and%20every%20time%20I%20sit%20to%20write%20on%20it%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20enter%20a%20time%20capsule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20I%20feel%20happy%20that%20she%20instilled%20the%20habit%20of%20writing%20in%20a%20diary%20in%20me.%20I%20too%20write%20regularly%2C%20if%20not%20daily.%20Always%20with%20my%20fountain%20pens%2C%20and%20this%20goes%20without%20saying%2C%20always%20with%20Sulekha%20Ink.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESreelekha%20Maitra%20is%20a%20creative%20marketing%20professional.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706611655000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30162100%2FScreenshot-2024-01-30-at-4.20.18%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsulekha-ink-history-tagore-gandhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20homegrown%20Sulekha%20Ink%2C%20named%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20and%20commissioned%20by%20Gandhi%2C%20became%20a%20sign%2C%20literally%2C%20of%20self-sufficiency%20in%20the%20days%20of%20the%20struggle%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fsulekha-ink-history-tagore-gandhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Want%20a%20happy%20and%20creative%20future%3F%20Spend%20more%20time%20longing%20for%20the%20past.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20business%20man%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20a%20TV%20with%20other%20nostalgic%20items%20around%20him%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b17a01617029e90a60242d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENostalgia%20doesn't%20hinder%20progress%2C%20it%20actually%20helps%20us%20move%20forward.%3Cp%3E4x6%2FGetty%2C%20shaunl%2FGett