20Congress%2C%20denied%20any%20plan%20to%20replace%20Mr%20Soren%20with%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20visuals%20of%20Mr%20Soren%20and%20his%20wife%20meeting%20MLAs%20played%20on%20TV%20screens%2C%20many%20were%20reminded%20of%20a%20precedent%20from%2026%20years%20ago%20and%20they%20wondered%3A%20is%20Hemant%20Soren%20trying%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20in%20Jharkhand%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShocking%20supporters%20and%20detractors%20alike%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20patriarch%20had%20got%20his%20wife%20Rabri%20Devi%20named%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20resign%20in%201997%20amid%20corruption%20allegations%20in%20the%20fodder%20scam.%20By%20the%20time%20he%20submitted%20his%20resignation%2C%20his%20supporters%20were%20raising%20slogans%20of%20%26quot%3BRabri%20Devi%20Zindabad%26quot%3B.%20The%20veteran%20socialist%20leader%20had%20then%20famously%20asked%20his%20aides%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20have%20forgotten%20me%20already%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20resigned%2C%20but%20remained%20in%20control%2C%20the%20only%20change%20being%20Rabri%20Devi's%20signature%20in%20government%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20left%20many%20awe-struck%20in%20its%20finesse%2C%20but%20also%20drew%20allegations%20of%20a%20ruthless%20urge%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20power%2C%20even%20if%20that%20required%20demolishing%20every%20edifice%20of%20political%20propriety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mr%20Soren's%20wife%20sat%20at%20the%20MLAs'%20meeting%2C%20the%20speculation%20that%20he%20was%20trying%20a%20repeat%20of%20that%20infamous%20move%20started%20doing%20the%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20resignation%20of%20a%20JMM%20MLA%20from%20the%20Assembly%2C%20citing%20personal%20reasons%2C%20was%20a%20precursor%20to%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Ahmed%2C%20JMM%20MLA%20from%20Gandey%2C%20resigned%20as%20MLA%20in%20January.%20He%20then%20told%20NDTV%20that%20he%20quit%20to%20strengthen%20the%20party%2C%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20and%20his%20leader%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%2C%20sources%20had%20then%20claimed%2C%20fears%20that%20the%20ED%20may%20arrest%20him%20and%20had%20planned%20to%20keep%20power%20in%20the%20family.%20If%20he%20is%20arrested%2C%20his%20wife%20can%20take%20over%20and%20be%20elected%20from%20the%20vacant%20Gandey%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJharkhand's%20MLA%20from%20Gandey%2C%20Sarfaraz%20Ahmed%2C%20has%20resigned%20from%20the%20Assembly%20and%20his%20resignation%20has%20been%20accepted.%20Soon%2C%20Hemant%20Soren-ji%20will%20also%20resign%20from%20the%20post%20of%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Kalpana%20Soren-ji%2C%20will%20take%20over%20as%20the%20next%20CM%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dubey%20had%20then%20said.%20The%20BJP%20had%20also%20urged%20the%20Governor%20to%20take%20legal%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20drama%20over%20Mr%20Soren's%20disappearance%20from%20public%20view%2C%20Jharkhand%20Governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan%20said%20he%20was%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20the%20development%20and%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20is%20above%20the%20law%26quot%3B.%20If%20Mr%20Soren%20tries%20a%20Lalu%20Yadav%20move%2C%20the%20Governor's%20role%20will%20be%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20is%20being%20investigated%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20racket%20of%20illegal%20change%20of%20land%20ownership%20by%20mafia%20in%20Jharkhand.%20The%20ED%20has%20arrested%2014%20people%20in%20the%20case%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20party%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20for%20political%20goals%20and%20questioned%20why%20a%20fresh%20summons%20was%20issued%20days%20after%20Mr%20Soren%20was%20questioned%20on%20January%2020.%20JMM%20has%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20ED%20for%20reaching%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Delhi%20residence%20with%20armed%20personnel%20yesterday%2C%20e