e-details%2Farticleshow%2F107257694.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IBM%20issues%20strict%20return-to-office%20policy%20requiring%20US%20managers%20to%20work%20from%20IBM%20office%20or%20client%20location%20at%20least%203%20days%20per%20week%3B%20IBM%20spokesperson%20emphasizes%20value%20of%20in-person%20collaboration%20for%20productivity%20and%20client%20service%3B%20CEO%20Arvind%20Krishna%20states%20remote%20employees%20will%20have%20fewer%20promotions%3B%20policy%20extends%20attendance%20requirements%20to%20all%20US%20managers%3B%20IBM%20continues%20restructuring%20efforts%3B%20badge-in%20data%20used%20to%20monitor%20office%20attendance%3B%20other%20companies%20like%20Amazon%20and%20AT%26amp%3BT%20also%20ask%20remote%20workers%20to%20relocate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Starts%205-Week%20H-1B%20Visas%20Renewal%20Drive%2C%20To%20Accept%2020%2C000%20Applications%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EH-1B%C2%A0workers%2C%20including%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20can%20begin%20applying%20to%20renew%20their%20visas%20without%20leaving%20the%20US%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20change%20after%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%2020%2C000%20qualified%20nonimmigrant%20workers%20can%20renew%20their%20H-1B%20visas%20domestically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20on%20the%20pilot%20program%20for%20in-country%20renewal%20of%20certain%20petition-based%20temporary%20work%20visas%2C%20including%20for%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20was%20made%20in%20June%202023%2C%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20visit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20announced%20at%20an%20Indian%20American%20community%20event%20in%20Washington%20that%20the%20H-1B%20visa%20renewal%20stamping%20was%20being%20conducted%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20joint%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20White%20House%20following%20the%20visit%20mentioned%20this%20development%2C%20indicating%20the%20commitment%20of%20both%20nations%20to%20streamline%20visa%20processes%20and%20facilitate%20the%20lives%20of%20temporary%20visa%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2020%2C000%20participants%20will%20be%20accepted%20for%20the%20pilot%20over%20the%20next%20five%20weeks%2C%20split%20equally%20between%20workers%20who%20recently%20received%20their%20H-1B%20specialty%20occupation%20visas%20at%20consulates%20in%20India%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20website%20released%20by%20the%20State%20Department%20ahead%20of%20the%20pilot's%20launch%20allowed%20visa%20holders%20to%20confirm%20their%20eligibility.%20Applicants%20could%20fill%20out%20a%20visa%20application%20form%20on%20the%20agency's%20website%20last%20week%2C%20although%20they%20couldn't%20be%20submitted%20until%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20thrilled%20to%20see%20the%20announcement%20that%20the%20State%20Department%20has%20officially%20launched%20the%20Visa%20Stamping%20initiative%20in%20the%20USA%20today.%20This%20endeavor%20aims%20to%20streamline%20and%20improve%20the%20visa%20process%20for%20legal%20immigrants%2C%20making%20it%20more%20efficient%20and%20less%20burdensome.This%20would%20eliminate%20the%20need%20for%20these%20applicants%20to%20travel%20abroad%20to%20renew%20visas%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajay%20Bhutoria%2C%20a%20prominent%20advocate%20for%20immigration%20issues%2C%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20this%20positive%20change%20will%20benefit%20thousands%20of%20the%20individuals%20invited%20to%20work%20in%20the%20US%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20our%20nation's%20companies%20and%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhaturia%20added.%20This%20pilot%20is%20one%20of%20the%20recommendations%20presented%20by%20Bhutoria%20of%20the%20President's%20Advisory%20Commission%20on%20Asian%20Americans%2C%20Native%20Hawaiians%2C%20and%20Pacific%20Islanders%2C%20which%20is%20now%20implemented%20by%20the%20State%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20for%20now%20is%20limited%20to%20only%20H-1B%20workers%20who%20meet%20the%20criteria%20outlined%20in%20December%20and%20excludes%20dependent%20visa%20holders%20like%20spouses%20and%20children%20on%20H-4%20visas--a%20source%20of%20frustration%20that%20many%20workers%20expressed%20when%20eligibility%20details%20emerged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutoria%20is%20also%20advocating%20for%20other%20important%20immigration%20reforms%2C%20including%20reducing%20the%20green%20card%20backlog%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DOS%20has%20indicated%20that%20the%20initial%20launch%20of%20this%20stateside%20visa%20renewal%20process%20will%20be%20a%20limited%20pilot%20program%20to%20test%20out%20the%20operationality%20of%20the%20program.%20If%20the%20pilot%20program%20proves%20successful%2C%20the%20DOS%20has%20expressed%20its%20strong%20desire%20to%20expand%20the%20program's%20eligibility%20to%20other%20visa%20categories%20and%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706605800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fjg7n7d98_h-1b-visa650-_625x300_05_August_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fus-starts-five-week-h-1b-visas-renewal-drive-to-accept-20-000-applications-4957808%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22H-1B%20workers%2C%20including%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20can%20begin%20applying%20to%20renew%20their%20visas%20without%20leaving%20the%20US%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20change%20after%20nearly%20two%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fus-starts-five-week-h-1b-visas-renewal-drive-to-accept-20-000-applications-4957808%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fus-starts-five-week-h-1b-visas-renewal-drive-to-accept-20-000-applications-4957808%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fus-starts-five-week-h-1b-visas-renewal-drive-to-accept-20-000-applications-4957808%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Photos%3A%20Students%20Protest%20UGC%20Proposal%20to%20De-Reserve%20Faculty%20Positions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30142410%2FMG_7807.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20has%20released%20new%20draft%20guidelines%20for%20recruitment%20for%20faculty%20positions%20in%20universities%2C%20sparking%20widespread%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20these%20guidelines%2C%20if%20no%20qualified%20candidates%20are%20identified%20for%20reserved%20seats%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20categories%2C%20those%20seats%20will%20be%20filled%20by%20candidates%20from%20the%20unreserved%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20a%20protest%20took%20place%20today%20in%20front%20of%20the%20UGC%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%2C%20denouncing%20the%20draft%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudent%20organisations%20from%20various%20colleges%20and%20universities%20in%20Delhi%20participated%20in%20this%20protest%2C%20with%20the%20Students%E2%80%99%20Federation%20of%20India%20(SFI)%2C%20Krantikari%20Yuva%20Sangathan%20(KYS)%2C%20All%20India%20Students%E2%80%99%20Association%20(AISA)%2C%20and%20Democratic%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20(DSU)%20prominent%20among%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20demonstration%2C%20students%20expressed%20their%20dissent%20against%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20UGC%2C%20raising%20slogans%20and%20displaying%20posters%20outlini