ual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107252198%2Cimgsize-21932.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fus-authority-fines-infosys-for-tax-violation-all-the-details%2Farticleshow%2F107252281.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Infosys%20receives%20%24225%20penalty%20from%20the%20Nevada%20Department%20of%20Taxation%20for%20underpaying%20modified%20business%20taxes%20in%20Q4%202021%20to%20Q1%202022.%20The%20company%20confirms%20receipt%20and%20is%20investigating%20the%20claim.%20Previous%20tax-related%20penalties%20include%20Florida%20(%2476.92)%20and%20Massachusetts%20(%241%2C101.96).%20Indian%20tax%20authorities%20demand%20Rs%2026.5%20lakh%20for%20non-payment%20of%20IGST.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gandhi%2C%20the%20Martyr%3B%20via%20J.P.S.%20Uberoi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05162325%2FMahatma_Gandhi_at_Bhangi_sweepers_colony_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20died%20a%20martyr%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Hindu%20fanatic%20Nathuram%20Godse%20on%20January%2030%2C%201948%2C%20not%20even%20a%20year%20after%20India%20had%20won%20its%20independence.%20The%20details%20of%20that%20event%20and%20its%20aftermath%2C%20including%20what%20we%20see%20unfolding%20before%20our%20eyes%20till%20today%2C%20have%20been%20discussed%20by%20social%20commentators%20and%20interpreters%20of%20history%20in%20detail%2C%20often%20with%20insight%20and%20not%20infrequently%20driven%20by%20intellectual%20guilt%20and%20obligation%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20gruesome%20murder%20of%20the%20father%20of%20the%20nation.%20However%2C%20this%20year%20the%20above%20date%20brings%20with%20it%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20student%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20truth%2C%20who%20though%20little%20read%20as%20an%20interpreter%20of%20Gandhi%2C%20came%20in%20my%20view%20the%20closest%20to%20extracting%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20Mahatma%20and%20his%20death%20for%20our%20times%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20figure%20in%20question%20is%20the%20sociologist%20Jitendra%20Pal%20Singh%20Uberoi%20(1934-2024)%2C%20fondly%20known%20to%20his%20colleagues%20and%20students%20as%20Prof%20Uberoi%20or%20just%20JPS%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20this%20January%203%20after%20living%20an%20extraordinary%20and%20exemplary%20life%20of%20thought%20and%20ideas%20as%20the%20longest%20serving%20professor%20(1969-1999)%20at%20the%20department%20of%20sociology%2C%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Uberoi%20is%20greatly%20admired%20by%20friends%20and%20enemies%20alike%20for%20his%20pioneering%20contributions%20to%20the%20study%20of%20European%20modernity%2C%20critical%20science%20studies%20and%20his%20study%20of%20religion%2C%20specifically%20Sikhism.%20Apart%20from%20his%20scholarly%20and%20in%20the%20true%20sense%20path-breaking%20writings%2C%20Professor%20Uberoi%20inspired%20generations%20of%20students%2C%20not%20only%20through%20the%20course%20of%20his%20formal%20employment%20for%20over%20three%20decades%20at%20the%20department%2C%20but%20subsequently%20too%20as%20the%20man%20of%2Fin%20the%20library%20(Ratan%20Tata%20Library)%2C%20which%20he%20continued%20to%20frequent%2C%20mostly%20without%20fail%2C%20till%20sometime%20in%20the%20year%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20insights%20offered%20in%20more%20formal%20settings%20like%20a%20classroom%20or%20as%20a%20supervisor%2C%20informal%20conversations%20with%20him%2C%20both%20pre%20and%20post-retirement%2C%20were%20strewn%20with%20breathtaking%20suggestions%20containing%20ideas%20and%20vignettes%2C%20which%20can%2C%20and%20did%20open%20new%20worlds%20for%20their%20listeners.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20sense%20Professor%20Uberoi%20inspired%20countless%20students%2C%20and%20thus%20remains%20the%20most%20remembered%20and%20revered%2C%20even%20though%20often%20misunderstood%20and%20shockingly%20little%20read%20teacher%20from%20the%20famed%20centre%20of%20sociology%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20going%20into%20the%20various%20dimensions%20of%20his%20multi-faceted%20and%20truly%20incomparable%20scholarship%2C%20in%20this%20short%20piece%20I%20want%20to%20highlight%20for%20his%20potential%20interlocutors%2C%20JPS%E2%80%99s%20fascinating%20engagement%20with%20Gandhi%2C%20particularly%20his%20tireless%20and%20consistent%20efforts%20to%20illuminate%20the%20meaning%20of%20his%20%3Cem%3Emartyrdom%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Ram%20Rajya%20Being%20Imagined%20Is%20Certainly%20not%20That%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmahatma-gandhi-angel-of-history-ram-rajya-ayodhya%5C%22%3EThe%20Ram%20Rajya%20Being%20Imagined%20Is%20Certainly%20not%20That%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20JPS%20never%20wrote%20a%20book%20%E2%80%98on%E2%80%99%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20to%20those%20who%20have%20read%20him%20or%20conversed%20with%20him%20his%20reading%20of%20Gandhi%20managed%20to%20present%20to%20us%20the%20most%20radical%20and%20strikingly%20sharp%20version%20of%20the%20Mahatma.%20What%20structured%20Professor%20Uberoi%E2%80%99s%20carefully%20thought%20out%20and%20committed%20probes%20was%20to%20give%20expression%20to%20the%20most%20robust%20and%20non-parochial%20understanding%20of%20%3Cem%3Eswaraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20his%20intellectual%20pursuits%2C%20taking%20a%20leaf%20out%20of%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20advocacy%20of%20the%20same%20in%20the%20fields%20of%20language%2C%20labour%20and%20culture%2C%20in%20short%20living%20a%20life%20of%20%3Cem%3Eswaraj%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20of%20self-rule%20and%20self-reform%2C%20at%20the%20university%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20a%20teacher-administrator%20as%20well%20as%20a%20well-wisher%20and%20interlocutor%20post%20his%20retirement%20in%201999.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferences%20to%20Gandhi%20are%20scattered%20across%20his%20oeuvre%2C%20which%20though%20appearing%20at%20the%20most%20surprising%20of%20places%2C%20including%20in%20his%20readings%20of%20science%20and%20Marxism%2C%20are%20part%20of%20a%20consistent%20system%20which%20most%20clearly%20inheres%20in%20his%20robust%20and%20unwavering%20application%20of%20the%20method%20he%20came%20to%20champion%20and%20christened%20the%20same%20as%20dialectical%20semiology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20said%20method%2C%20unlike%20the%20structuralism%20of%20France%2C%20involved%20a%20non-dualist%20search%20for%20mediations%20between%20supposedly%20opposed%20entities%20like%20science%20and%20politics%2C%20fact%20and%20value%2C%20and%20that%20much%20abused%20one%2C%20nature%20and%20culture.%20As%20an%20example%20of%20a%20text%20similar%20in%20spirit%20to%20Uberoi%E2%80%99s%20method%2C%20as%20mentioned%20and%20discussed%20by%20him%20only%2C%20is%20Friedrich%20Engels%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EDialectics%20of%20Nature%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20the%20only%20difference%20being%20that%20as%20compared%20to%20Engels%20and%20other%20later%20day%20dialecticians%20he%20was%20as%20sensitive%20to%20the%20symbolism%20of%20labour%20as%20to%20its%20instrumentality.%20Readers%20will%20note%20that%20a%20non-dualist%20understanding%20of%20symbol%20and%20instrument%20also%20set%20him%20apart%20from%20the%20later%20day%20semiologists%20who%20were%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20Engels%2C%20more%20absorbed%20in%20the%20issues%20of%20sign%20and%20symbolism%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20work%20and%20labour.%20To%20rush%20to%20a%20conclusion%20here%20due%20to%20the%20paucity%20of%20space%2C%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Enothing%20if%20not%20this%20method%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20Professor%20Uberoi%3B%20a%20method%20or%20principle%20behind%20mediation%20and%20not%20merely%20a%20search%20for%20a%20balanced-middle.%20With%20these%20remarks%2C%20which%20are%20only%20suggestive%2C%20I%20would%20now%20like%20to%20discuss%20briefly%20JPS%E2%80%99s%20most%20direct%20engagement%20with%20Gandhi%2C%20which%20as%20I%20began%20this%20article%20with%2C%20concerns%20his%20martyrdom%20and%20the%20astute%20professor%E2%80%99s%20remarkable%20attempt%20to%20outline%20a%20comparative%20sociology%20and%20theology%20of%20martyrdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fbook%2F35213%2Fchapter-abstract%2F299703482%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%3Estudies%20of%20Sikhism%20and%20Islam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20religion%20more%20broadly%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20expository%20work%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1177%2F0038022919990102%3FjournalCode%3Dsoba%5C%22%3Econcept%20of%20civil%20society%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0JPS%20accorded%20to%20martyrdom%20the%20agency%20which%20was%20only%20cursorily%20associated%20with%20it%2C%20owing%20to%20its%20mistaken%20identification%20with%20violence%20and%20destruction.%20JPS%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20thinks%20of%20martyrdom%20as%20a%20prime%20mover%20of%20society%20and%20history%3B%20a%20harbinger%20of%20salvation-in-society%20through%20non-violent%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Indian%20modernity%2C%20saint-poets%20like%20Kabir%20and%20Nanak%20sounded%20and%20led%20an%20ushering%20of%20a%20revolution%20in%20the%20fields%20of%20language%20(vernacular)%2C%20labour%20(artisanal%20crafts)%20and%20liturgy%20(direct%20communion%20with%20God-in-society)%2C%20literally%20creating%20in%20process%20a%20mediating%20civil%20society%20as%20against%20the%20priest%20(Brahmin)%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20the%20prince%20(Rajput)%20on%20the%20other.%20Professor%20Uberoi%20methodically%20and%20with%20sound%20purpose%20equates%20the%20discourse%20of%20Indian%20modernity%20with%20the%20emergence%20and%20subsequent%20strengthening%20of%20Sikhism%20and%20what%20by%20implication%20he%20calls%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98modern-Indian%E2%80%99%20religion%20(and%20not%20Hinduism%2C%20Islam%20or%20Sikhism%20taken%20in%20isolation)%3B%20a%20form%20of%20religion%20which%20%3Cem%3Edefines%3C%2Fem%3E%20society%20and%20protects%20its%20unity-in-variety%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20uniform%20and%20homogenising%20tendencies%20of%20power.%20Professor%20Uberoi%20appends%20the%20long%20list%20of%20martyrs%20who%20had%20laid%20down%20their%20lives%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98truth%E2%80%99%20of%20Indian%20modernity%2C%20which%20he%20admirably%20delineates%20for%20us%20in%20a%20series%20of%20sparkling%20essays%2C%20with%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20Gandhiji.%20Here%20a%20few%20clarificatory%20remarks%20on%20the%20institution%20of%20martyrdom%20will%20be%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F07103747%2Fimage-1692.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22801%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F07103747%2Fimage-1692.png%20801w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F07103747%2Fimage-1692-300x117.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691877%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22312%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EProfessor%20J.P.S.%20Uberoi%20(%20September%205%2C%201934%20%E2%80%93%20January%203%2C%202024).%20Photo%3A%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%2FWikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarking%20back%20to%20the%20twin%20meanings%20of%20the%20Urdu%20word%20%3Cem%3Eshahid%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20witness%20and%20the%20martyr%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fbook%2F35213%2Fchapter-abstract%2F299703830%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%3EJPS%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20martyrs%20are%20essentially%20witnesses%20or%20testimony-givers%20for%20the%20truth%20of%20the%20cause%20which%20betokens%20them.%20This%20cause%20has%20to%20be%20judged%20and%20evaluated%2C%20and%20in%20Professor%20Uberoi%E2%80%99s%20rendering%20it%20more%20often%20than%20not%20comes%20down%20to%20the%20right%20of%20a%20people%20to%20congregation%20and%20to%20follow%20the%20calling%2C%20whether%20religious%20or%20secular%2C%20that%20the%20congregation%20chooses%20for%20itself.%20The%20martyr%2C%20embodying%20twin%20principles%20of%20representation%20and%20vicariousness%2C%20lays%20down%20their%20life%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20group%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20resurrection%20of%20both%20the%20group%20and%20the%20truth%20it%20is%20based%20on.%20Giving%20oneself%20in%20self-sacrifice%2C%20through%20suffering%20and%20non-violence%20the%20martyr%20bears%20testimony%20to%20the%20manyness%20yet%20indivisibility%20of%20truth%2C%20a%20part%20of%20which%20is%20apportioned%20to%2Fby%20their%20group.%20They%20are%20not%20only%20representatives%20of%20their%20groups%2C%20but%20also%20in%20their%20act%20others%20may%20find%20refuge%20and%20forgiveness%20of%20their%20sins%2C%20hence%20the%20principle%20of%20vicariousness.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20sense%20that%20Gandhi%20was%20the%20martyr%20par%20excellence%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Sikh%20gurus%2C%20Imam%20Husain%20and%20Jesus%20Christ%2C%20and%20figures%20such%20as%20John%20Lambert%20in%20the%20modern%20period.%20But%20what%20was%20Gandhi%20a%20martyr%20for%3F%20JPS%E2%80%99s%20unequivocal%20answer%20is%2C%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20national%20civil%20society.%20However%2C%20before%20JPS%20can%20wager%20this%20answer%20he%20needs%20to%20place%20the%20concept%20of%20civil%20society%20on%20surer%20footings%20than%20on%20which%20it%20has%20been%20placed%20by%20academic%20scholarship%20and%20this%20he%20does%20with%20style%20and%20creativity%20befitting%20his%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUberoi%20noted%20that%20civil%20society%20has%20always%20been%20thought%20of%20as%20a%20domain%20betwixt%20and%20between%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Church%2C%20and%20seldom%20as%20an%20autonomous%20arena%20generating%20and%20sustained%20by%20its%20own%20custom%2C%20which%20pertains%20not%20only%20to%20professional%2C%20but%20also%20and%20equally%20to%20ethical%20and%20religious%20life.%20The%20integral%20plurality%20of%20institutions%20constituting%20civil%20society%20(a%20domain%20which%20has%20been%20narrowly%20viewed%20as%20a%20domain%20to%20be%20governed)%20and%20the%20salvational%20possibilities%20it%20creates%20through%20associated%20living%2C%20with%20the%20right%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20and%20unstinting%20regard%20for%20one%E2%80%99s%20neighbour%E2%80%99s%20labour%2C%20combined%20with%20peaceful%20coexistence%20with%20equally%20forceful%2C%20yet%20simultaneously%20incomplete%20and%20partial%20truths%20forming%20its%20core%2C%20has%20been%20ignored%20both%20in%20the%20dominant%20liberal%20and%20Marxist%20traditions.%20Whereas%20in%20the%20former%20it%20often%20plays%20a%20second-fiddle%20to%20market%20and%20politics%2C%20in%20the%20latter%20it%20is%20reduced%20to%20the%20playing%20field%20of%20class-conflicts%20and%20the%20hegemonic%20consensus%20which%20eventually%20overpowers%20or%20smoothens%20them.%20As%20against%20this%2C%20and%20drawing%20out%20the%20possibilities%20inherent%20in%20figures%20as%20diverse%20as%20Hegel%20and%20Marx%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20and%20Bhakti%20saints%20and%20poets%20on%20the%20other%2C%20JPS%20pins%20down%20civil%20society%20as%20the%20true%20domain%20of%20self-realisation%20and%20by%20implication%20of%20self-rule%20such%20that%20both%20tradition%20and%20authority%2C%20as%20against%20custom%20and%20usage%2C%20are%20reduced%20to%20playing%20a%20minimalistic%20role%20in%20the%20life%20and%20progress%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Story%20of%20Two%20Temples%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-valmiki-temple-birla-caste%5C%22%3EMahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20Story%20of%20Two%20Temples%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20such%20civil%20society%2C%20positively%20informed%20by%20religion%20as%20%3Cem%3Esewa%20%3C%2Fem%3Einstead%20of%20religion%20as%20cultural%20identity%2C%20and%20hence%20consistently%20and%20principally%20avoiding%20the%20path%20of%20either%20state-established%20religion%20or%20religion-established%20state%2C%20that%20Gandhi%20laid%20his%20life%20for%3B%20a%20civil%20society%20corresponding%20to%20genuine%20federalism%20and%20sincere%20respect%20for%20all%20faiths%20and%20their%20corresponding%20truths.%20A%20civil%20society%20moreover%20which%20is%20not%20just%20a%20category%20of%20bourgeois%20society%20or%20modern%20capitalism%2C%20but%20a%20universal%20human%20institution%20presencing%20as%20per%20its%20own%20logic%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20contexts%2C%20globally%20and%20historically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJPS%E2%80%99s%20Gandhi%20comes%20across%20like%20a%20rockstar%2C%20much%20like%20JPS%20himself%20was.%20His%20Gandhi%20is%20quirky%20and%20exacting%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20his%20sheer%20novelty%20of%20thought%20and%20practice%20shines%20through%20whatever%20JPS%20wrote%2C%20even%20though%20the%20writing%20in%20question%20may%20not%20directly%20concern%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20life%20or%20career.%20Whether%20it%20is%20his%20passionate%20defence%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2012%2F32%2Fspecial-articles%2Fmarxism-labour-or-property.html%5C%22%3Elabour%20theory%20of%20value%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fedition%2FThe_Other_Mind_of_Europe%2FVrfaAAAAMAAJ%3Fhl%3Den%26gbpv%3D1%26bsq%3Dthe%2Bother%2Bmind%2Bof%2Beurope%26dq%3Dthe%2Bother%2Bmind%2Bof%2Beurope%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%5C%22%3Eunearthing%20of%20the%20alternate%20science%20of%20Goethe%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20face%20of%20dominant%20Newtonian-ism%2C%20Gandhi%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20vantage%20point%20from%20which%20Professor%20Uberoi%20thinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20in%20my%20view%20rehabilitates%20Gandhi%20in%20a%20way%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20direct%20commentary%2C%20whether%20critical%20or%20hagiographic%2C%20could%20ever%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20as%20we%20see%20the%20crisis%20of%20Indian%20civil%20society%2C%20not%20to%20say%20of%20state%20and%20spirituality%2C%20unfolding%20before%20our%20eyes%20one%20wonders%20what%20remains%20alive%20of%20Gandhian%20martyrdom%20and%20its%20defence%20by%20true-spiritual%20disciples%20like%20JPS.%20As%20the%20prince%20and%20the%20priest%20become%20one%20again%2C%20recalling%20to%20the%20mind%20the%20institution%20of%20divine%20kingship%20as%20studied%20by%20James%20Frazer%2C%20in%20the%20zealously%20active%20role%20played%20by%20the%20state%20in%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%3B%20as%20the%20institutions%20of%20civil%20society%2C%20including%20the%20courts%20and%20judiciary%20cower%20down%20to%20the%20executive%20and%20comply%20to%20the%20tunes%20sung%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be%3B%20as%20the%20universities%20lose%20their%20way%2C%20submitting%20themselves%20to%20the%20logic%20of%20either%20state%20or%20market%20and%20thus%20increasingly%20not%20able%20to%20carry%20forward%20independent%20traditions%20of%20inquiry%20and%20knowledge%20creation%3B%20as%20organisations%20such%20as%20the%20various%20small%20and%20big%20NGOs%20are%20breathing%20their%20last%20due%20to%20the%20state%20directed%20drying%20up%20of%20funds%20and%20other%20supports%3B%20and%20as%20the%20position%20of%20informal%20labour%20slides%20to%20ever%20greater%20depths%3B%20reading%20JPS%20and%20Gandhi%20via%20him%20is%20simultaneously%20depressing%20and%20hope-inducing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20one%20agrees%20or%20disagrees%20with%20JPS%20or%20Gandhi%20for%20that%20matter%2C%20it%20dawns%20upon%20one%E2%80%99s%20conscience%20that%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20death%20was%20a%20gift%20India%20was%20not%20ready%20to%20receive%20and%20has%20never%20fully%20accepted%20ever%20since.%20Gandhi%20embodied%20a%20truth%20which%20was%20not%20just%20his%2C%20but%20of%20a%20project%20which%20encapsulated%20India%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20its%20own%20modernity%3B%20a%20truth%20which%20the%20civil%20society%20in%20post-independence%20India%20has%20always%20struggled%20to%20internalise%20and%20seems%20to%20have%20finally%20given%20up%20on.%20In%20this%20context%20one%20recalls%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.oup.com%2Facademic%2Fproduct%2Fmind-and-society-9780199495986%3Fcc%3Dus%26lang%3Den%26%23%5C%22%3EJPS%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20the%20Editor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(dated%20October%2030%2C%201984)%2C%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20Punjab%20problem%20(as%20viewed%20by%20the%20state)%20and%20a%20day%20before%20the%20assassination%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20where%20he%20makes%20a%20distinction%20between%20Gandhian%20and%20non-Gandhian%20secularists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latter%2C%20he%20suggests%2C%20as%20they%20are%20forever%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20statist%20logic%20of%20majority%20and%20minority%2C%20are%20not%20able%20to%20spell%20out%20an%20agenda%20for%2C%20to%20use%20JPS%E2%80%99s%20own%20terms%2C%20%E2%80%98stronger%20philosophical%20digestion%20and%20stronger%20social%20institutions%E2%80%99.%20The%20Gandhian%20variant%20of%20secularism%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20premised%20on%20the%20cherished%20principle%20of%20unity-in-variety%20and%20the%20pursuit%20of%20Truth-and-God-in-society%2C%20gives%20us%20a%20formula%2C%20yet%20to%20be%20fully-successfully%20tried%20out%2C%20for%20combining%20a%20multi-religious%20nation%20with%20a%20federal-secular%20state%3B%20the%20combining%20instrument%20being%20a%20robust%20and%20philosophically%20secure%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gandhi%20and%20the%20Future%20of%20Slow%20Philosophy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fgandhi-and-the-future-of-slow-philosophy%5C%22%3EGandhi%20and%20the%20Future%20of%20Slow%20Philosophy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20thoughts%20like%20these%20and%20others%20to%20the%20same%20effect%20are%20read%2C%20even%20if%2C%20in%20fact%20particularly%20if%20by%20practising%20and%20believing%20Hindus%20outside%20the%20precincts%20of%20the%20academia%2C%20JPS%E2%80%99s%20work%20and%20the%20Gandhi%20which%20it%20attempts%20to%20salvage%20for%20us%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20look%20them%20into%20the%20eyes%20and%20ask%20about%20their%20moral-courage%20regarding%20the%20right%20to%20define%20their%20faith%20in%20their%20own%20way%20and%20not%20be%20treated%20merely%20as%20a%20handmaiden%20of%20the%20executive%20branch%20of%20the%20state.%20In%20fact%20the%20stirring%20plea%20implicit%20in%20Professor%20JPS%20Uberoi%E2%80%99s%20work%20to%20revisit%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20faith%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3Emethod%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20the%20fate%20of%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20and%20society%20has%20to%20be%20reimagined%20cannot%20be%20emphasised%20enough.%20In%20this%20body%20of%20work%20lies%20the%20most%20sustained%20articulation%20of%20the%20truth%20of%20Gandhi%2C%20including%20the%20ordered%20anarchy%20of%20civil%20society%20the%20Mahatma%20most%20consistently%20advocated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeast%20of%20all%2C%20and%20most%20humbly%2C%20Professor%20Uberoi%E2%80%99s%20sociology%20can%20enable%20us%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20the%20loss%20many%20of%20us%20feel%20in%20contemporary%20times%2C%20but%20are%20unable%20to%20articulate%20a%20coherent%20response%20in%20the%20face%20of%20it.%20It%20teaches%20us%20to%20look%20at%20it%20squarely%20in%20the%20face%20before%20a%20response%2C%20particularly%2C%20and%20here%20I%20am%20talking%20as%20a%20teacher%20and%20researcher%20of%20sociology%2C%20a%20scholarly%20and%20intellectual%20response%20can%20be%20wagered.%20Measuring%20up%20to%20the%20challenge%20in%20a%20manner%20somewhat%20close%20to%20what%20JPS%20accomplished%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20anti-Sikh%20pogrom%20of%201984%20by%20unravelling%20for%20his%20interlocutors%20and%20detractors%2C%20the%20truth%20of%20religion%2C%20particularly%20Sikhism%20as%20against%20the%20Hindudom%20of%20a%20Savarkar%20which%20threatened%20to%2C%20and%20still%20does%20with%20much%20greater%20alacrity%20than%20ever%2C%20overpower%20religion%2C%20civil%20society%20and%20the%20state%20in%20India.%20And%20if%20the%20lesson%20of%20martyrdom%2C%20as%20understood%20by%20Gandhi%20and%20drawn-out%20by%20JPS%20for%20the%20social-sciences%2C%20is%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20a%20struggle%20and%20sacrifice%20at%20one%20frontier%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20liberating%20consequences%20for%20all%20institutions%20in%20civil%20society%3B%20representatively%20and%20vicariously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20end%20with%2C%20I%20am%20unable%20to%20resist%20recalling%20an%20anecdote%20of%20a%20conversation%20with%20Professor%20Uberoi%20under%20the%20expansive%20and%20generous%20fig%20tree%20outside%20the%20RTL.%20While%20on%20one%20his%20swan%20songs%20on%20history%20and%20society%20in%20India%20he%20looked%20at%20me%20with%20his%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20piercing%20and%20kind%20eyes%2C%20and%20said%20in%20his%20deep%20voice%20%3Cem%3Eek%20hi%20to%20Hindu%20tha%20aur%20aapne%20use%20maar%20diya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(there%20was%20only%20one%20Hindu%20and%20you%20killed%20him).%20He%20further%20added%20that%20the%20name%20of%20%3Cem%3ERama%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Gandhi%20had%20on%20his%20lips%20when%20he%20died%20was%20most%20profoundly%20that%3B%20a%20%3Cem%3Ename%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20mode%20of%20intersubjective%20address%20through%20which%20the%20lord%20and%20the%20devotee%20revel%20in%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20co-presence%20as%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Edidar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20loving%20call%20of%20address%20and%20remembrance%2C%20and%20not%20just%20a%20deity%20belonging%20to%20or%20claimed%20by%20a%20particular%20group%2C%20but%20a%20metaphysical%20ideal%20shared%20across%20traditions.%20Some%20of%20these%20words%20found%20their%20way%20into%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fbook%2F35213%2Fchapter-abstract%2F299703881%3FredirectedFrom%3Dfulltext%5C%22%3Edeeply%20insightful%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20theory%20of%20the%20name%20and%20Indian%20modernity%3B%20a%20paper%20he%20was%20working%20on%20in%20the%20RTL%20when%20I%20used%20to%20consistently%20interact%20with%20him%20while%20studying%20for%20MPhil%20(Sociology)%20at%20DSchool%20(2011-2013).%20One%20reads%20this%20and%20other%20such%20papers%20today%20and%20is%20not%20only%20struck%20by%20the%20premonition%20JPS%20had%20regarding%20what%20the%20name%20of%20%3Cem%3ERama%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come%2C%20but%20also%20by%20the%20sincere%20urgency%20with%20which%20he%20tried%20to%20ring%20the%20true%20sense%20of%20the%20same%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20life%20and%20martyrdom%2C%20Professor%20Uberoi%E2%80%99s%20scholarship%20is%20also%20a%20%3Cem%3Egift%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20the%20question%20arises%20are%20we%20ready%20to%20receive%20it%3F%20A%20further%20question%20follows%3B%20if%20not%20now%2C%20then%2C%20when%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaumya%20Malviya%20is%20Assistant%20Professor%20(Sociology)%2C%20School%20of%20Humanities%20and%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20Mandi%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20India.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706596222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05162325%2FMahatma_Gandhi_at_Bhangi_sweepers_colony_New_Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fgandhi-the-martyr-via-j-p-s-uberoi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year%20January%2030%20brings%20with%20it%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20student%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20his%20truth%2C%20who%20tho