h%E2%80%99s%20writ%20petition%20and%20the%20division%20bench%E2%80%99s%20Letters%20of%20Patent%20Appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Letter%20of%20Patent%20Appeal%20is%20a%20petition%20against%20a%20single%20judge%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20a%20different%20bench%20of%20the%20same%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2F41222024150149991order29-jan-2024-519077.pdf%5C%22%3EOn%20January%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0apex%20court%20judges%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20apparent%20clash%20between%20Justices%20Gangopadhyay%20and%20Sen%2C%20observing%20that%20any%20remark%20would%20demean%20the%20dignity%20of%20a%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CCasting%20aspersions%20on%20a%20single%20judge%20or%20division%20bench%20would%20not%20be%20proper.%20Anything%20we%20say%20will%20affect%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20High%20Court.%20We%20will%20handle%20it%20in%20some%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20CJI%2C%20decided%20to%20transfer%20the%20entire%20matter%20to%20itself%2C%20scheduling%20it%20for%20a%20three-week%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20representing%20the%20Bengal%20government%2C%20flagged%20an%20%E2%80%9Congoing%20concern%E2%80%9D%20over%20Justice%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20who%20consistently%20handles%20similar%20cases.%20The%20judge%20has%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20over%20some%20of%20his%20judgments%20which%20do%20not%20favour%20her%20administration.%20He%20had%20earlier%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbengal-ssc-recruitment-scam-how-a-focused-judge-exposed-the-racket%5C%22%3Eexposed%20a%20teacher%20recruitment%20exam%20racket%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C