ss%20his%20personal%20God%2C%20in%20the%20film%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20cry%20of%20dismay%20at%20the%20atrocities%20committed%20in%20his%20God%E2%80%99s%20name%20that%20Ram%20would%20never%20have%20accepted.%20The%20cry%20is%20also%20a%20conscience%20raiser%20and%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20poignantly%20suggestive%20of%20how%20we%20have%20killed%20the%20Ram%20within%20us%20by%20becoming%20complicit%20with%20Hindutva%20ideological%20forces.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cry%20thus%20designates%20both%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20horror%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20outrages%20man%20can%20commit%20on%20man%20and%20also%20constitutes%20an%20appeal%20to%20bring%20those%20%E2%80%9Chorrors%E2%80%9D%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30104823%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30104823%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30104823%2Fmaxresdefault-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30104823%2Fmaxresdefault-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694878%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20still%20from%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20child%20God%20installed%20in%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20cannot%20be%20associated%20with%20the%20horrors%20mentioned%20above%2C%20and%20will%20elicit%20a%20protective%2C%20almost%20maternal%20love%20from%20his%20devotees%2C%20the%20forces%20unleashed%20by%20his%20coming%20to%20occupy%20the%20temple%20have%20already%20caused%20a%20trail%20of%20destruction%20and%20violence%20as%20some%20cadres%20of%20Hindutva%20regimes%20go%20about%20wreaking%20havoc.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20inauguration%2C%20these%20forces%20have%20burnt%20and%20destroyed%20houses%20and%20properties%20of%20Muslims%2C%20violently%20disrupted%20programmes%20that%20remember%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-babri-masjid-demolition-went-unpunished-and-the-fight-for-justice-died%5C%22%3Edemolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20and%20in%20intentionally%20provocative%20and%20humiliating%20gestures%20have%20challenged%20and%20dared%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20playing%20songs%20of%20victory%20outside%20a%20mosque.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20use%20another%20film%20example%20%E2%80%93%20that%20culminates%20in%20the%20inauguration%20of%20a%20new%20Ram%20temple%20to%20illustrate%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20communal%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20physical%2C%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20%E2%80%93%20impacts%20the%20lives%20of%20Muslims%20on%20an%20everyday%20level.%20In%20Zaigham%20Imam%E2%80%99s%202019%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENakkash%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Allah%20Rakha%20is%20a%20sculptor%20and%20engraver%20who%20has%20spent%20his%20life%20engraving%20the%20walls%20of%20temples%20in%20Benaras%20and%20nearby%20areas.%20This%20is%20a%20profession%20that%20is%20hereditary%20and%20he%20has%20learnt%20the%20art%20from%20his%20father.%20The%20film%20traces%20the%20communal%20tensions%20that%20build%20up%20in%20the%20city%20before%20an%20election%2C%20while%20Allah%20Rakha%20remains%20dedicated%20to%20completing%20the%20gold%20engraved%20wall%20of%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20with%20beautiful%20idols%20of%20Ram%2C%20Lakshman%20and%20Sita.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20siz