A%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhika%20urges%20women%20to%20have%20big%20dreams%20and%20not%20give%20up%20on%20them.%20She%20shares%20that%20she%20embraced%20motherhood%20at%2039%2C%20and%20manages%20money%20and%20diapers%20with%20equal%20elan.%20To%20women%20confused%20about%20how%20to%20manage%20work%20and%20home%20or%20when%20to%20have%20a%20baby%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20fall%20for%20the%20debate%2C%20and%20do%20things%20as%20per%20your%20time%20and%20will.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mom%20gave%20me%20the%20best%20piece%20of%20advice%20on%20motherhood.%20She%20told%20me%20that%20no%20mother%20is%20a%20bad%20mother.%20You%20can%20be%20poor%2C%20rich%2C%20educated%2C%20uneducated%2C%20working%2C%20not%20working%2C%20but%20not%20a%20bad%20mother.%20Another%20piece%20of%20advice%20is%20that%20motherhood%20is%20a%20big%20part%20of%20your%20life%2C%20and%20six%20months%20is%20just%20a%20small%20part%20of%20your%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20her%20leadership%2C%20Edelweiss%20Asset%20Management%20Limited%20currently%20manages%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20crore.%20She%20is%20looking%20to%20invest%20in%20young%20companies%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20part%20of%20the%20show%2C%20she%20says%20she%20feels%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335548%2Fthis-hero-turned-mud-walls-into-blackboards-streets-into-schools-for-10000-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeels%20optimistic%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20India%2C%20seeing%20the%20limitless%20potential%20of%20the%20young%20entrepreneurs%20on%20the%20show.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20takeaway%20from%20the%20show%20for%20me%20has%20been%20the%20fact%20that%20young%20Indians%20are%20truly%20limitless.%20And%20they%20are%20from%20Tier%203%20and%204%20towns%20of%20the