I%20had%20recognised%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20small%20idea%20sprung%20into%20my%20head.%20I%20started%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20where%20I%20invited%20people%20to%20segregate%20their%20waste%20and%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20me%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20goody%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20it%20worked!%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20showed%20so%20much%20interest%20and%20were%20willing%20to%20do%20it%20for%20a%20reward.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20and%20interesting%20concept%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20sign%20enough%20and%20Abhishek%20decided%20to%20expand%20on%20this%20idea.%20%E2%80%9CA%20small%20family%20of%20people%2C%20everyday%20400%20to%20500%20gm%20of%20plastic%20is%20generated%20at%20home.%20There%20are%20no%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310812%2Fmukul-chhabra-scrapuncle-delhi-startup-collects-recycles-scrap-wins-lakhs-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20scrap%20dealers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20will%20take%20that%20amount%20of%20plastic.%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20was%20a%20problem%20with%20many%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20push%20people%20to%20make%20segregating%20waste%20a%20habit%20and%20part%20of%20their%20daily%20routine%2C%20Abhishek%20decided%20to%20give%20them%20an%20incentive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20idea%20behind%20Goodeebag%20came%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20Agarwal%2C%20Founder%20of%20Goodeebag.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651.jpg%20