gle%20boy%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20painter%20with%20disabilities%2C%20these%2019%20children%20have%20been%20bestowed%20with%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%202024%20for%20their%20exceptional%20achievements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20awardees%20comprising%2010%20girls%20and%20nine%20boys%20were%20conferred%20with%20the%20award%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%2022%20January%202024%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20on%2026%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20the%20list%20of%2019%20kids%20who%20were%20awarded%20for%20showcasing%20exceptional%20bravery%2C%20innovative%20thinking%2C%20artistic%20prowess%2C%20and%20selfless%20social%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAaditya%20Vijay%20Bramhane%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2012-year-old%2C%20who%20hailed%20from%20the%20Nandurbar%20district%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20sacrificed%20his%20life%20to%20rescue%20his%20cousins%20from%20drowning%20after%20they%20fell%20into%20a%20river%20while%20playing.%20For%20his%20incredible%20act%20of%20bravery%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Bravery%20Awards%20posthumously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArijeet%20Banerjee%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2013-year-old%20from%20West%20Bengal%20was%20conferred%20for%20his%20exceptional%20skills%20in%20playing%20the%20traditional%20Pakhawaj.%20Previously%2C%20Arijeet%20has%20received%20accolades%20such%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20M%20S%20Subbulakshmi%20Fellowship%20and%20has%20been%20included%20in%20the%20Asia%20Book%20of%20Records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20presented%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar.%20The%20President%20said%20that%20children%20and%20youth%20are%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20future%20of%20our%20country.%20It%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20make%20them%20aware%20of%20Indian%20cultur